Place Piper .onnx and .json model files here.

Expected naming convention:
    en_US-lessac-medium.onnx
    en_US-lessac-medium.json
    es_ES-davefx-medium.onnx
    es_ES-davefx-medium.json

NOTE: Spanish (es) models serve as the Tagalog voice — no native
tl_PH Piper model is available. The backend routes Tagalog requests
through the Spanish model under the hood.

Model files can be downloaded from:
    https://huggingface.co/rhasspy/piper-voices
